---
title: Pineapple Cheesecake & Coconut Caramel with Oat Crumble  | Serves 4
description: Close your eyes and allow the taste of a sunset to wash over you when you bite into this sweet pineapple cheesecake. Drizzle over as
much coconutty caramel sauce as you want, this whole cheesecake is a slice of paradise.

*We’ve replaced the tinned mango in this recipe with tinned pineapple due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66c81faab372008c572c3719-346284ed.jpeg
